- All malloc/calloc calls checked for NULL return
- All array accesses bounds-checked
- All strings null-terminated
- Buffer sizes validated before copy, fread, memchr operations
- All allocated memory freed exactly once
- No arithmetic on pointers from user input
- Integer overflow checks before arithmetic
- All function return values checked
- Sensitive data cleared before free, USE memset_s function instead of memset 
"],
